data.description: Attention Builders.  Rare opportunity to build a dream home with access to Lake Nabnasset.  This property contains three parcels of land totaling 35,875 square feet.  55 Lawson Rd (Parcel One) contains 16,715 square feet of land with a year-round 4 room,2 bedroom, 1 bath cottage with 864 sq ft of living space.  Parcel Two, also known as Parcel A, Map 0073, Parcel 146 is a vacant lot containing 15,000 square feet of land.  Parcel Three, Map 0073, Parcel 142 containing 4,160 square feet of land with 53 feet of frontage on Lake Nabnasset.  Seller is including the dock on Parcel Three along with a pontoon boat and trailer.  Seller has done Perc test on Parcel Two, all engineering and permits are the responsibility of the buyer.
